{"uuid": "a8974554-0561-4610-955e-02ffcad00459", "id": 13044, "date": "2019-10-20T05:00:00", "date_gmt": "2019-10-20T12:00:00", "guid": {"rendered": "http://estreetshuffle.com/?p=13044"}, "modified": "2019-10-20T06:02:22", "modified_gmt": "2019-10-20T13:02:22", "slug": "matr-roy-orbison-and-bruce-springsteen-only-the-lonely-know-the-way-i-feel", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2019/10/20/matr-roy-orbison-and-bruce-springsteen-only-the-lonely-know-the-way-i-feel/", "title": {"rendered": "MatR: Roy Orbison and Bruce Springsteen, Only the Lonely (Know the Way I Feel)"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p>Blink and you&#8217;ll miss him, but that&#8217;s Bruce sitting behind Roy Orbison playing guitar in this clip from Roy&#8217;s 1987 concert film,&nbsp;<em>Roy Orbison &amp; Friends: A Black &amp; White Night</em>.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Roy Orbison - &quot;Only the Lonely&quot; from Black and White Night\" width=\"758\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/4YG__LBJVZ0?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p>Bruce was one of Roy&#8217;s &#8220;friends&#8221; that night (along with Elvis Costello, Jackson Browne, and a host of other stellar musicians), and although Bruce didn&#8217;t get much screen time on this first song of the evening, he more than made up for it throughout the night. (Watch more great performances from that evening <a href=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/?s=orbison+black+white+night\">here</a>.)</p>\n<p>As for the original song, that was Roy&#8217;s first big hit upon its release in the spring of 1960. It stopped just shy of the top spot in the U.S., but it made it all the way to #1 in the U.K.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Roy Orbison - Only The Lonely\" width=\"758\" height=\"569\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/kjq4wYuwgxs?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n<p>Despite the song&#8217;s popularity and Bruce&#8217;s lifelong admiration of Roy, though, that all-star line-up in 1987 represents the only time Bruce has ever performed &#8220;Only the Lonely&#8221; live.</p>\n<p><strong>Only the Lonely (Know the Way I Feel)</strong><br />\n<strong>First performed:</strong> September 30, 1987 (Los Angeles, CA)<br />\n<strong>Last performed:</strong> September 30, 1987 (Los Angeles, CA)</p>\n<p>Watch more great performances from <em>Roy Orbison and Friends: A Black &amp; White Night </em><a href=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/?s=orbison+black+white+night\">here</a>.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>One time only: Bruce joins Roy Orbison and an all-star line-up on Roy&#8217;s first big hit, &#8220;Only the Lonely.&#8221;</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 13282, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "ena